{"tid":1303921,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同A0既女仔拍拖真係好慘","createTime":"2019-07-10T12:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T18:21:18.000Z","uid":243691,"like":89,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a6721da1e6a778913e94740a27b029140012af55","tid":1303921,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"事先聲明 未同過A0既男仔拍拖 唔知慘唔慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA0既女仔 一開始溝既時候 其實已經好格硬<br />\n周不時9唔搭8 用佢自己一套唔成熟既想法去量度你<br />\n拍拖果陣會幻想你做好多浪漫野 你冇做佢就會好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幻想例如有好似白馬王子咁日日接佢放工<br />\n時時刻刻有事冇事都要聽佢電話<br />\n都算 唔識分輕重我都當你細路女未識諗<br />\n但係有時佢以為可以用對你閪黎逼你就範<br />\n真係R撚晒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643ef71d711080d16724af6a942f568fbdc674d0","tid":1303921,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"去到今日我都係r撚晒頭"},{"pid":"fd1a46515680a9f1fcde3354d434a9e1509e63e4","tid":1303921,"uid":256205,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"分手咪得囉屌"},{"pid":"d8877ecc33c662edbf155635e22ee3d45d4f430d","tid":1303921,"uid":243691,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"fd1a46515680a9f1fcde3354d434a9e1509e63e4","tid":1303921,"uid":256205,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"分手咪得囉屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"一早散左 忍佢咩"},{"pid":"ba4342f87abc5700336c03a14f3a4d8d9dc87fb2","tid":1303921,"uid":56323,"like":27,"dislike":0,"